               <p>ROBERT FISHER. I am a <rs id="t18300916-249-viclabel1275" type="occupation">cork-cutter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-249-victim2045 t18300916-249-viclabel1275"></join>, and live in Aldermanbury - I have known the prisoner three or four years - he was occasionally in my employ. On the 18th of June I sent him from my house to fetch a bundle of cork from <placeName id="t18300916-249-crimeloc1276">Ryder's-court, Leicester-fields</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18300916-249-crimeloc1276" type="placeName" value="Ryder's-court, Leicester-fields"></interp>
