                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-249-off1273 t18300916-249-crimeloc1276"></join>; I gave him a sovereign to pay for it, and lent him my knot and hat - he never returned, but came in July, and I gave him in charge- he said he had lost the sovereign, and worn the hat out in doing porter's work at different markets, and was ashamed to return - I applied at his lodging the night this happened; he was not at home.</p>
